            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Decent infrastructure, however like many other schools these days, the homework, assignments etc are encouraged with gadgets. Web, laptops for kids should be avoided/discouraged but school doesn't show the maturity to discourage kids from using (or getting addicted to) gadgets.\nThankfully kids are not allowed mobile phones.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
