          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "2",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "School Infrastructure is really good, the amount of equipment available for activities and sports is impressive.\nBut when it comes to learning, it's all unhinged.\nStudents are taught from poorly made PPTs, there is 0 transparency and no proper means of communication, students are pressurized with homework, classrooms are not modern, A/C is not provided, fans are noisy, washrooms are no better than public washrooms, not sure why, even after having the funds, they refuse to develop these changes in the school...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
